The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Montys plea to Sourav: 

 Hum bacche hain

Its not known what Monty Panesar told Mahendra Singh Dhoni, after he clouted him for two sixes on Friday, but hed pleaded with Sourav Ganguly when he smashed him over the rope on Day I. 

 According to chief selector Dilip Vengsarkar, dheere 

 marna, hum bacche hain, is what Panesar said at 

 the end of that over. 

 With Ian Howell claiming Sourav, the left-arm spinner 

 got spared. Not for too long, though. 

 OUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT IN LONDON 




